#, no-wrap
msgid "Check if the bug is already known\n"
msgstr "Revisa si el error ya ha sido notificado\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "Have a look at:"
msgstr "Echa un vistazo en:"

#. type: Bullet: '  - '
msgid "the [[list of known issues|support/known_issues]]"
